1
00:00:05,672 --> 00:00:06,798
Why did you do that?

2
00:00:08,299 --> 00:00:09,843
Do what?

3
00:00:11,344 --> 00:00:13,471
Why did you fight instead of me?

4
00:00:14,556 --> 00:00:15,807
Who do you think you are?

5
00:00:19,102 --> 00:00:21,521
Do you want to go to the holding cell again?

6
00:00:24,858 --> 00:00:26,985
Are you always like this?

7
00:00:28,486 --> 00:00:29,821
How did you know?

8
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:39,622
Is that important?

9
00:00:50,925 --> 00:00:52,343
Hangyeol.

10
00:00:53,428 --> 00:00:55,180
Someone's messing with my person,

11
00:00:56,306 --> 00:00:59,559
what crazy guy would just stay still?

12
00:01:05,565 --> 00:01:09,986
It's really easy to make someone look like a fool.

13
00:01:11,946 --> 00:01:14,157
You have strong pride, you know.

14
00:01:15,075 --> 00:01:17,243
Your wounds that you didn't want to show...

15
00:01:18,453 --> 00:01:21,581
I didn't want to just carelessly say I knew about them.

16
00:01:25,752 --> 00:01:26,961
That's all.

17
00:01:33,343 --> 00:01:35,845
You weren't shaken?

18
00:01:37,889 --> 00:01:39,724
By the rumors?

19
00:01:43,645 --> 00:01:45,355
Me? Why?

20
00:01:47,899 --> 00:01:50,318
I waited.

21
00:01:51,528 --> 00:01:53,571
For you to sort things out,

22
00:01:53,571 --> 00:01:57,617
and tell me yourself someday...

23
00:02:01,454 --> 00:02:04,165
But I'm sorry.

24
00:02:06,167 --> 00:02:07,293
For not contacting you

25
00:02:07,293 --> 00:02:10,296
and making you wait aimlessly.

26
00:02:11,673 --> 00:02:16,636
I didn't know that would become a wound too.

27
00:02:40,076 --> 00:02:42,912
I won't let you go anymore.

28
00:02:45,582 --> 00:02:48,668
Now I'll hold onto you.

29
00:03:51,773 --> 00:03:53,900
I missed you.

30
00:04:19,217 --> 00:04:20,134
Hangyeol.

31
00:04:21,094 --> 00:04:24,514
It's snowing like crazy here in Gangwon-do.

32
00:04:24,514 --> 00:04:26,474
Since coming to the army,

33
00:04:26,474 --> 00:04:28,559
I think I shovel snow more than I train.

34
00:04:28,559 --> 00:04:30,520
How did you endure this?

35
00:04:30,520 --> 00:04:32,772
Ah, I told you to stop reading~

36
00:04:35,483 --> 00:04:37,944
Ah, what a waste.

37
00:04:37,944 --> 00:04:38,987
What is?

38
00:04:38,987 --> 00:04:42,282
That I'm reading these fun letters only now.

39
00:04:42,282 --> 00:04:44,325
This is funnier than stand-up comedy.

40
00:04:44,325 --> 00:04:46,119
See?

41
00:04:46,119 --> 00:04:47,745
Who told you to move without a word?

42
00:04:47,745 --> 00:04:49,747
And change your number too?

43
00:04:56,462 --> 00:04:58,840
If this letter had arrived properly back then,

44
00:04:59,549 --> 00:05:01,801
would we have not broken up?

45
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:03,678
Who knows?

46
00:05:03,678 --> 00:05:05,179
Do you think waiting for a boyfriend in the army is easy?

47
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:11,019
But how did you keep all these letters?

48
00:05:11,019 --> 00:05:14,939
That jerk Jaeseop had them. Guess he felt guilty.

49
00:05:14,939 --> 00:05:16,774
I heard he visited your place a few times.

50
00:05:17,317 --> 00:05:18,693
But since I found out way later,

51
00:05:18,693 --> 00:05:21,362
I was seriously pissed off.

52
00:05:21,362 --> 00:05:24,657
No really, I almost became a 'soldier of concern' in the army.

53
00:05:24,907 --> 00:05:27,744
I suffered too, you know.

54
00:05:27,910 --> 00:05:28,911
I wasn't even in the army,

55
00:05:28,911 --> 00:05:31,331
I lived alone abroad.

56
00:05:33,249 --> 00:05:34,042
Living alone abroad,

57
00:05:34,042 --> 00:05:36,127
do you know how hard that is?

58
00:05:36,753 --> 00:05:38,254
But why Japan?

59
00:05:39,047 --> 00:05:41,132
You said you'd transfer to our university.

60
00:05:43,301 --> 00:05:46,054
I was afraid you'd come find me.

61
00:05:46,929 --> 00:05:49,140
Afraid Hyung would come find me.

62
00:05:49,557 --> 00:05:52,977
That you'd throw away your pride and everything to come.

63
00:05:54,354 --> 00:05:57,023
Do you know the taste of Takoyaki when you eat it crying?

64
00:05:57,732 --> 00:05:59,984
You're really cruel, Lee Hangyeol.

65
00:05:59,984 --> 00:06:02,362
So be good to me.

66
00:06:02,362 --> 00:06:04,447
If I get upset,

67
00:06:05,239 --> 00:06:08,117
I'm going to eat Takoyaki alone.

68
00:06:08,117 --> 00:06:11,079
I'm sorry, okay?

69
00:06:11,662 --> 00:06:13,373
I'm sorry, hmm?

70
00:06:14,248 --> 00:06:18,252
I think I'm going to really hate winter from now on.

71
00:06:18,252 --> 00:06:19,087
Let's stop reading.

72
00:06:19,087 --> 00:06:24,217
You hate winter?

73
00:06:28,846 --> 00:06:31,682
Seems like you two are back together.

74
00:06:33,768 --> 00:06:35,603
It turned out that way.

75
00:06:36,521 --> 00:06:37,939
Why do you keep smiling?

76
00:06:38,356 --> 00:06:39,649
It's annoying.

77
00:06:40,983 --> 00:06:42,235
It's thanks to you, Yuchan.

78
00:06:43,528 --> 00:06:46,155
For staying by Hangyeol's side

79
00:06:46,155 --> 00:06:48,783
and doing what I couldn't do.

80
00:06:50,743 --> 00:06:52,161
Forget it.

81
00:06:53,538 --> 00:06:55,748
I just did what I wanted to do.

82
00:06:58,418 --> 00:06:59,877
But...

83
00:07:01,295 --> 00:07:03,339
seeing Hangyeol laugh,

84
00:07:04,298 --> 00:07:06,759
makes me feel good.

85
00:07:07,969 --> 00:07:10,054
Still, thank you.

86
00:07:12,932 --> 00:07:15,393
If only Jaeseop hadn't caused a drunken scene that day...

87
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:18,062
Why did I even drink...

88
00:07:18,896 --> 00:07:20,857
You should tell him to fix his drinking habits.

89
00:07:20,857 --> 00:07:22,233
Exactly.

90
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,110
Hey, you're not even a party involved,

91
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,194
talking like that, huh?

92
00:07:25,194 --> 00:07:27,530
Is it okay to talk about others like that?

93
00:07:31,617 --> 00:07:34,245
Take good care of him.

94
00:07:34,537 --> 00:07:36,998
Of Hangyeol.

95
00:07:36,998 --> 00:07:40,960
Yes, I promise.

96
00:07:41,586 --> 00:07:44,797
Or else I'm taking him back.

97
00:08:01,063 --> 00:08:02,940
Back then and now,

98
00:08:04,609 --> 00:08:07,069
you still leave your clothes lying around anywhere.

99
00:08:22,668 --> 00:08:23,294
Huh?

100
00:08:23,294 --> 00:08:25,755
Hyung, when did you get here?

101
00:08:25,755 --> 00:08:27,965
Just now.

102
00:08:41,812 --> 00:08:43,439
What were you doing just now?

103
00:08:43,439 --> 00:08:44,690
Like a pervert.

104
00:08:45,066 --> 00:08:48,069
What pervert...

105
00:08:51,531 --> 00:08:54,575
It's been a long time smelling Hyung's scent.

106
00:08:54,575 --> 00:08:56,118
Right, a pervert.

107
00:09:04,001 --> 00:09:07,380
Have you ever seen such a pretty pervert?

108
00:09:11,008 --> 00:09:15,721
Did you get prettier than before?

109
00:09:22,436 --> 00:09:24,605
What's with that all of a sudden?

110
00:09:29,151 --> 00:09:31,862
This time, really without regrets,

111
00:09:31,862 --> 00:09:34,073
laugh a lot,

112
00:09:34,073 --> 00:09:36,951
be honest,

113
00:09:36,951 --> 00:09:40,621
travel anywhere together,

114
00:09:40,621 --> 00:09:41,455
and for a long, long time

115
00:09:41,455 --> 00:09:43,749
stay by my side.

116
00:09:53,426 --> 00:09:56,470
Let's date.

117
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:58,806
Park Jeongwoo.

118
00:10:40,848 --> 00:10:41,974
Hyung!

119
00:10:45,144 --> 00:10:46,729
Sunglasses?

120
00:10:46,729 --> 00:10:48,773
How is it? Cool, right?

121
00:10:48,773 --> 00:10:50,232
Just bought them.

122
00:10:50,232 --> 00:10:51,901
Hmm... we're going to Jeju,

123
00:10:51,901 --> 00:10:53,736
isn't that too flashy?

124
00:10:54,111 --> 00:10:55,363
If you don't like it, forget it.

125
00:10:55,363 --> 00:10:57,490
Hyung must not want to put in effort.

126
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:59,825
I didn't say I don't like it.

127
00:11:03,204 --> 00:11:04,872
Shall we go?

128
00:11:04,872 --> 00:11:05,998
Yeah.

129
00:11:05,998 --> 00:11:07,541
I'll carry it.
